OL,3,CMinute-by-minute accounts of horrified
OL,4,Cresidents during Hainault sword rampage
OL,6,FMore details have been confirmed by
OL,7,Fpolice about how the fatal sword
OL,8,Fattack in east London unfolded.JThe
OL,9,Fhorror began when a man crashed a van
OL,10,Finto a fence in Laing Close, Hainault
OL,11,Fjust before 7am, hitting a 33-year-
OL,12,Fold, before stabbing him in the neck.
OL,13,FResidents described "a huge commotion"
OL,14,Fand hearing shouts and screams.JThe
OL,15,Fswordman then attacked a 35-year-old
OL,16,Fman in a nearby home, leaving him with
OL,17,Finjuries to his arm.JWitnesses
OL,18,Fdescribed the suspect talking to a
OL,19,Fwoman and asking her to confirm his
OL,20,Flocation to someone on the phone,
OL,21,Fbefore she saw the sword and fled.
