OL,3,CMinute-by-minute accounts of horrified
OL,4,Cresidents during Hainault sword rampage
OL,6,FJames Fernando, 39, said: "She's
OL,7,Frealised something isn't right,
OL,8,Fstarted running and he's pulled a
OL,9,Fsamurai sword from the back of his
OL,10,Ftrousers.J"She's shouted to the other
OL,11,Fneighbour - a Nigerian boy who was on
OL,12,Fhis way to school."JIt was then that
OL,13,Fthe attacker fatally wounded 14-year-
OL,14,Fold Daniel Anjorin.JMr Fernando said
OL,15,Fthe suspected killer was running
OL,16,Faround looking for more victims.JAs
OL,17,Fpolice officers raced to stop him,
OL,18,Farriving 12 minutes after the first
OL,19,F999 call, they tried to use
OL,20,Fincapacitant spray and Tasers but both
OL,21,Fhad little effect, the Metropolitan
OL,22,FPolice said.JThe suspect went on to
OL,23,Fseriously injure two police officers,
OL,24,Fboth of whom required surgery on
OL,25,FTuesday and remain in hospital.
