OL,6,FOne female officer suffered severe
OL,7,Finjuries to her arm and nearly lost a
OL,8,Fhand, while a male colleague suffered
OL,9,Fserious wounds to his hand.JOne woman
OL,10,Fwho lives nearby said: "We were very
OL,11,Fscared and trying to hide and not show
OL,12,Fourselves through the window because
OL,13,Fhe was standing right next to our
OL,14,Fhouse and he could have seen us if he
OL,15,Flooked up.J"We were trying to hide but
OL,16,Falso at the same time taking video of
OL,17,Fhim attacking the police, and of the
OL,18,Fbody on the floor, so, yeah, we were
OL,19,Fvery scared and we didn't know what to
OL,20,Fdo."
