OL,6,FThe suspect then fled again, with
OL,7,Fterrified witnesses hiding as he
OL,8,Fclimbed over garden fences.JOther
OL,9,Fofficers surrounded him in Thurlow
OL,10,FGardens and managed to use Taser to
OL,11,Foverpower him.
OL,13,FThe video shows how officers shout at
OL,14,Fthe suspect, saying "Don't move, don't
OL,15,F******* move" after he's brought to
OL,16,Fthe ground by three separate Taser
OL,17,Fdischarges.JHe was arrested and taken
OL,18,Fto hospital for injuries caused when
OL,19,Fhe crashed the van.
